Returns whether the specified vehicle is currently in a burnout.


vb.net
Public Function isVehicleInBurnout(vh As Vehicle) As Boolean
        Return Native.Function.Call(Of Boolean)(Hash.IS_VEHICLE_IN_BURNOUT, vh)
    End Function
